				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: The Minimum Wage Debate Continues</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-02-19T17:42:25+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">February 19, 2014 12:42 pm</time>
